386→                        <div id="content">Find the best function $f(d)$ such that, in any 2-colouring of the integers, at least one colour class contains an arithmetic progression with common difference $d$ of length $f(d)$ for infinitely many $d$.</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/187">#187</a>: <a href="#cite-Er73-187" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er73','187'); return false;">[Er73]</a><a href="#cite-ErGr79-187" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('ErGr79','187'); return false;">[ErGr79]</a><a href="#cite-ErGr80-187" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('ErGr80','187'); return false;">[ErGr80,p.17]</a></div>
